<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<odoo>
    <template id="ipushp.iPushp" name="ipushp">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <div class="">
                <section
                    class="s_fix_bg_snippet s_fix_bg_option s_fix_bg_snippet"
                    style="height:100vh;"
                >
                    <div class="container-fluid s_fix_bg_title text-center">
                        <span>i P u s h p</span>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="s_title mt64 mb64">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <h3
                                    class="text-center o_default_snippet_text"
                                    style="text-shadow: 0.9px 0.9px wheat;"
                                >A
                                    <b>P</b>
                                    rogram for the
                                    <b>U</b>
                                    pliftment of the
                                    <b>S</b>
                                    erpentCS families for their
                                    <b>H</b>
                                    armony,
                                    <b>P</b>
                                    rosperity and welfare.</h3>
                                <h4
                                    class="text-center text-muted o_default_snippet_text"
                                >This assures the growth of the family, not an individual working at SerpentCS.</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="s_title mt64 mb64" style="background: beige;">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt16">
                                <h1
                                    style="text-shadow: 3px 1px wheat;"
                                >About Program</h1>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-12 col-md-offset-1 font20 mt16 mb64">
                                <p
                                    class="text-muted o_default_snippet_text"
                                >Everyone carries a unique talent and when this talent is utilised in the profession and utilised for the betterment of family, this shines up like a GOLD. We, at SerpentCS have thought of generating an internal activity among families of SerpentCS which will enlighten the spirit of families and this will turn into the revenue generation and towards the ease of life.</p>
                                <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt16">
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center"
                                    >अयं निजो परो वेति गणना लघुचेतसाम्।</h4>
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center"
                                    >उदारचरितानां तु वसुधैव कुटुम्बकम्॥</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-12 text-center mt16">
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center"
                                    >The small-minded count this is mine and that is someone else's |</h4>
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center"
                                    >For the men of great character, the whole world is their family ||</h4>
                                </div>
                                <p
                                    class="text-muted o_default_snippet_text"
                                    style="text-align: justify;"
                                >From Day 1, SerpentCS has always kept ‘Vasudhaiva Kutumbakam’ feeling in the roots. We have always wanted the upliftment of the families of the SerpentCS member. Keeping all aspects of Indian culture in mind, we have been always working for the equal growth of the families. This time, we are putting that system on roll and we are launching the program for the same purpose.</p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-muted o_default_snippet_text"
                                >Be it a tailor, beautician, tutor, teacher, doctor, banker,  jeweller, carpenter, actor, singer, dancer, or any personal business that will touch the lives of others and can help you earn respect and monetary gains; if any of the above skill is within your family, you are going to get a business within the company. The number of assured customers for you/family are 3 times equal to the no. of employees.</p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-muted o_default_snippet_text"
                                >Being a part of SerpentCS, you have a privilege to connect an another world and even possible to launch the services of your family online by any means. </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <section class="teamblock">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row ">
                            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                                <h1
                                    style="text-shadow: 3px 1px wheat;"
                                >Program Teams</h1>
                                <div class="divider" />
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="pv-30 ph-20 service-block bordered shadow text-center object-non-visible animated object-visible fadeInDownSmall float-left"
                                data-animation-effect="fadeInDownSmall"
                                data-effect-delay="100"
                            >
                                <span class="icon bg-df circle">
                                    <i class="fa fa-male" />
                                </span>
                                <h4>Vinay Vandara</h4>
                                <div class="divider clearfix" />
                                <p>vinay.vandra@serpentcs.com</p>
                                <p>+91 9909913165</p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="pv-30 ph-20 service-block bordered shadow text-center object-non-visible animated object-visible fadeInDownSmall float-right"
                                data-animation-effect="fadeInDownSmall"
                                data-effect-delay="100"
                            >
                                <span class="icon bg-df circle">
                                    <i class="fa fa-female" />
                                </span>
                                <h4>Dhwani Vora</h4>
                                <div class="divider clearfix" />
                                <p>d.vasavada.serpentcs@gmail.com</p>
                                <p>+91 9662768877</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div id="registration_section" />
                <t t-if="request.session.uid">
                    <section class="s_title mt64" id="">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                                    <h1
                                        style="text-shadow: 3px 1px wheat;"
                                    >Program Registration</h1>
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center o_default_snippet_text mt16"
                                    >Here, we will publish a program where everyone can subscribe and register their family/familyperson business and get the benefit</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-12 mt32 mb64 s-signup">
                                    <form
                                        action="/contact_ipushp"
                                        class="s_website_form form-horizontal container-fluid mt32"
                                        method="post"
                                    >
                                        <input
                                            name="csrf_token"
                                            t-att-value="request.csrf_token()"
                                            type="hidden"
                                        />
                                        <input
                                            id="user_id"
                                            name="user_id"
                                            t-att-value="uid"
                                            type="hidden"
                                        />
                                        <div
                                            class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                        >
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="business_categ_id"
                                            >Business Category</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <select
                                                    class="select_business_categ form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="business_categ_id"
                                                    required="True"
                                                    title="Business Category"
                                                >
                                                    <option
                                                        class="default_option"
                                                        default="default"
                                                        label=""
                                                    />
                                                    <option
                                                        t-att-selected="error and len(error) &gt; 0 and new_category_id == -1"
                                                        value="-1"
                                                    >-- Create a new Category --</option>
                                                    <t t-if="category_data">
                                                        <t
                                                            t-as="company"
                                                            t-foreach="category_data"
                                                        >
                                                            <option
                                                                t-att-data-code="company.name"
                                                                t-att-value="company.id"
                                                            >
                                                                <t
                                                                    t-esc="company.name"
                                                                />
                                                            </option>
                                                        </t>
                                                    </t>
                                                </select>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form_so_new_shipp hidden">
                                            <div
                                                class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                            >
                                                <label
                                                    class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                    for=""
                                                >Category Name</label>
                                                <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                    <input
                                                        class="form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                        name="category_name"
                                                        type="text"
                                                    />
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div
                                            class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                        >
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="relation_id"
                                            >Your Relation</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <select
                                                    class="select_relation form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="relation_id"
                                                    required="True"
                                                    title="Your Relation"
                                                >
                                                    <option
                                                        class="default_option"
                                                        default="default"
                                                        label=""
                                                    />
                                                    <t t-if="relation_data">
                                                        <t
                                                            t-as="company"
                                                            t-foreach="relation_data"
                                                        >
                                                            <option
                                                                t-att-data-code="company.name"
                                                                t-att-value="company.id"
                                                            >
                                                                <t
                                                                    t-esc="company.name"
                                                                />
                                                            </option>
                                                        </t>
                                                    </t>
                                                </select>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div
                                            class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                        >
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="name"
                                            >Name</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <input
                                                    class="form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="name"
                                                    required=""
                                                    t-att-value="request.params.get('contact_name', '')"
                                                    type="text"
                                                />
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group form-field">
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="phone"
                                            >Phone Number</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <input
                                                    class="form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="phone"
                                                    t-att-value="request.params.get('phone', '')"
                                                    type="text"
                                                />
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div
                                            class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                        >
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="email"
                                            >Email</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <input
                                                    class="form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="email"
                                                    required=""
                                                    t-att-value="request.params.get('email_from', '')"
                                                    type="text"
                                                />
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div
                                            class="form-group form-field o_website_form_required_custom"
                                        >
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="description"
                                            >Description</label>
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <textarea
                                                    class="form-control o_website_form_input"
                                                    name="description"
                                                    required=""
                                                />
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group form-field">
                                            <label
                                                class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 control-label"
                                                for="description"
                                            />
                                            <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                                                <button
                                                    class="btn btn-primary"
                                                    type="submit"
                                                >Submit</button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </t>
                <t t-if=" not request.session.uid">
                    <section class="s_title mt64" id="">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                                    <h1
                                        style="text-shadow: 3px 1px wheat;"
                                    >Program Registration</h1>
                                    <h4
                                        class="text-center mt64 mb32"
                                        style="font-style: italic;"
                                    >Please login to program registration!</h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class=" col-md-12 mb64 text-center">
                                    <a
                                        class="btn btn-primary "
                                        href="/web/login"
                                        type="button"
                                    >Login</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </t>
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>
    <template id="ipushp_thanks" name="Thank you from iPushp">
        <t t-call="website.layout">
            <div id="wrap">
                <div class="oe_structure" />
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Thanks!</h1>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-8">
                            <div
                                class="alert alert-success"
                            >Your details has been sent successfully.

                                <button
                                    class="close"
                                    data-dismiss="alert"
                                    type="button"
                                >&amp;times;</button></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <t t-call="website.company_description" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="oe_structure" />
            </div>
        </t>
    </template>
</odoo>
